This topic describes the prerequisites for installing and configuring NSX Data Center v3 for VMware Tanzu Kubernetes Grid Integrated Edition (TKGI) on vSphere.  

##<a id='nsxt30-prereqs'></a> Prerequisites for Installing VMware NSX

To perform a new installation of VMware NSX for Tanzu Kubernetes Grid Integrated Edition, complete the following steps in the order presented.

1. Read the [Release Notes](./release-notes.html) for the target TKGI version you are installing and verify NSX v3 support.

1. Read the topics in the [Preparing to Install Tanzu Kubernetes Grid Integrated Edition on vSphere with VMware NSX](./vsphere-nsxt-index-prepare.html) section of the documentation.
